# Build context for the rat daemon image (core/Dockerfile → core + contracts) AND the
# plugin images (examples/<plugin>/Dockerfile, platform/bff → examples/platform + the
# python SDK). Allow those trees; aggressively exclude the heavy junk (examples/ alone is
# ~59M of node_modules/__pycache__ otherwise).
*
!core
!contracts
!examples
!platform
examples/**/node_modules
examples/**/__pycache__
examples/**/*.vsix
platform/**/__pycache__
**/target
**/logs
**/.git
